<p>1.	Information on how to enter and prize details form part of these conditions.  Purchase of any of the Eligible Games during the Promotion Period constitutes acceptance of the terms and conditions of the Promotion.</p>
<p>2.	The Promoter is Telstra Corporation Limited ABN 33 051 775 556 of 151 Clarence Street, Sydney, NSW 2000.</p>
<p>3.	The Promotion will be open from 9:00am Australian Eastern Daylight-savings Time ("AEDT") on 7 November 2008 and will continue until 5:00pm AEDT on 3 December 2008 ("Promotion Period").  </p>
<p>4.	Entry is open to all Australian residents aged 18 years and over who are Telstra pre-paid or post-paid mobile customers with a mobile phone handset capable of supporting any of the Eligible Games (listed in clause 26) other than management, employees or contractors of the Promoter and other agencies, firms or companies associated with the Promotion (including suppliers of prizes), and their immediate families ("Eligible Entrants").  </p>
<p>5.	To enter and be eligible to win, Eligible Entrants must complete one of the Options below during the Promotion Period.  All steps in an Option must be completed in the one transaction.</p>
<p>Option One:</p>
<p>(a)	go to the BigPond Games website at www.bigpondgames.com ("Website");</p>
<p>(b)	click on the "Buzz Competition" link;</p>
<p>(c)	choose "Buzz Competition" or one of the other Eligible Games listed in clause 26 and select to buy the game from the Promoter; and</p>
<p>(d)	when prompted, SMS the supplied game code to 176 to receive a link to download the game; or</p>
<p>Option Two:</p>
<p>(a)	access the BigPond Games WAP site ("WAP Site") via their Telstra mobile phone service;</p>
<p>(b)	click on the "Buzz Competition" banner; and </p>
<p>(c)	choose "Buzz Competition" or one of the other Eligible Games listed in clause 26 and select to buy the game from the Promoter,</p>
<p>	(each Option constitutes an "Eligible Purchase"). </p>
<p>6.	Eligible Entrants who complete an Eligible Purchase will be automatically entered into the Promotion ("Eligible Entry").  Eligible Entrants will be entered into the Promotion as many times as they make an Eligible Purchase.  The entrant will be deemed the account holder of the mobile phone used to make the Eligible Purchase.</p>
<p>7.	Eligible Entrants who are in breach of the BigPond Games terms and conditions at any time between the start of the Promotion Period and the Draw Date will be ineligible to win a prize.  These terms and conditions are available at http://www.telstra.com.au/customerterms/docs/infoservices.pdf.</p>
<p>8.	In Option One the cost of sending a SMS message will not exceed 55 cents.  Standard browsing charges apply, where applicable, in accessing the WAP Site under Option Two.</p>
<p>9.	A computerised draw for the prizes will take place at 10:00am AEDST on 4 December 2008  ("Draw Date") at Anisimoff Legal, Suite 1, Level 1, 34 Chandos Street, St Leonards, NSW 2065 ("Draw Location").  The draw will be conducted by a representative of Anisimoff Legal.</p>
<p>10.	The Eligible Entrants with the first and second valid Eligible Entries drawn will each win from the Promoter a Sony Buzz prize pack valued at $1,107.90 (GST inclusive) consisting of:</p>
